These files are for the semnsor and Laser enclosure (boxes) and the base they fit into.

21/04/2026 The recess in the base was made to fit the AliExpress table I ordered, which was 88mm x 88mm.

However it was reported that a recent table purchased was 90mm x 90mm. Therefore the recess for the table has been increased in size to 91mm x 91mm.
